## 🚀 Instalasi

### Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- Node.js atau Web Browser modern
- SQLite3

### Langkah-Langkah Instalasi

#### 1. Clone Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Zuel25/adaptive-learning-system.git
cd adaptive-learning-system
```

#### 2. Setup Backend
```bash
# Masuk folder backend
cd backend

# Buat virtual environment (opsional tapi disarankan)
python -m venv venv

# Aktivasi virtual environment
# Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
# Mac/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

#### 3. Jalankan Backend
```bash
# Dari folder backend
python app.py
```

Server akan berjalan di `http://localhost:5000`

#### 4. Setup Frontend
```bash
cd ../frontend

# Gunakan Live Server atau HTTP Server
# Opsi 1: Dengan Python (Python 3)
python -m http.server 8000

# Opsi 2: Dengan Node.js (jika terinstall)
npx http-server -p 8000
```

Akses aplikasi di `http://localhost:8000`

## 🎮 Menjalankan Aplikasi

### Terminal 1 - Backend
```bash
cd backend
python app.py
```

### Terminal 2 - Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
python -m http.server 8000
```

### Buka Browser
Akses `http://localhost:8000` di browser

## 📁 Struktur Project

```
adaptive-learning-system/
├── frontend/
│   ├── index.html              # Halaman login
│   ├── student/
│   │   ├── pretest.html        # Pre-test numerasi
│   │   ├── learning.html       # Materi pembelajaran
│   │   └── practice.html       # Latihan soal
│   ├── teacher/
│   │   └── dashboard.html      # Dashboard guru
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css           # Styling utama
│   └── js/
│       ├── app.js              # Main logic
│       └── api.js              # API integration
├── backend/
│   ├── app.py                  # Flask server utama
│   ├── database.py             # Database setup & queries
│   ├── ai_model.py             # AI/ML logic
│   ├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
│   └── adaptive_learning.db    # SQLite database (auto-created)
└── README.md                   # Dokumentasi
```

